Overview When conducting your empirical research, you typically spend a lot of time cleaning and documenting your data so that team members can use it.
Several open science tools can help you manage the process of cleaning, documenting, and - importantly - maintaining your dataset more efficiently. For this, we require a &ldquo;data workflow.&rdquo;
